CommunicationMode model is an evaluation model. An evaluation model holds a "question" in the key and holds a coded value (CD) answer in data. For example, in the HairColorEval model, the "question" is "What is the hair color evaluation?", and the "answer" in data can be "White".
In theCommunicationMode model, the question is "what is the subject's communication mode?" and the coded answers can be expressed written, expressed signed, received spoken.
CommunicationMode by definition means the person's method of expressing language.  


